  <front>
    <title>Redesignation of 240/4 from "Future Use" to "Private Use"</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-wilson-class-e-02"/>
    <author initials="P." surname="Wilson" fullname="Paul Wilson">
      <organization>APNIC</organization>
    </author>
    <author initials="G. G." surname="Michaelson" fullname="George G. Michaelson">
      <organization>APNIC</organization>
    </author>
    <author initials="G." surname="Huston" fullname="Geoff Huston">
      <organization>APNIC</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="29" month="September" year="2008"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document directs the IANA to designate the block of IPv4
addresses from 240.0.0.0 to 255.255.255.255 (240.0.0.0/4) as unicast
address space for Private Use.
	 </t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
